description: This file defines utility matchers and predicates for comparing instances of the Note class, including methods for comparing by id and visible content.

classes.name: NoteMatchers
classes.description: Utility class providing static methods for matching Note instances based on specific criteria.

methods.name: sameId
methods.description: Checks if two notes have the same id, considering null safety.

methods.name: sameVisibleContent
methods.description: Checks if two notes have the same visible content (title, content, pinned, color).
